WEBVTT

00:03.069 --> 00:06.071
<i>In last week's episode of</i> Soap,
<i>Chester had a plan.</i>

00:06.072 --> 00:08.073
<i>To keep from being lonely</i>
<i>in the basement,</i>

00:08.074 --> 00:10.576
<i>he made friends with a pet rat</i>
<i>named Arnold.</i>

00:10.577 --> 00:12.578
<i>Unfortunately,</i>

00:12.579 --> 00:14.079
<i>Benson didn't know he was a pet.</i>

00:14.080 --> 00:15.581
<i>This ruined Chester's plan...</i>

00:15.582 --> 00:18.083
<i>not to mention any plans</i>
<i>Arnold might have had.</i>

00:18.084 --> 00:19.585
<i>Meanwhile,</i>

00:19.586 --> 00:21.587
<i>Burt told Danny a plan</i>
<i>to help him change Elaine.</i>

00:21.588 --> 00:24.089
<i>And Carol told Jody her plan</i>
<i>to keep the baby.</i>

00:24.090 --> 00:25.591
<i>Tim and Corinne's plan</i>
<i>for their wedding night</i>

00:25.592 --> 00:27.092
<i>was interrupted</i>

00:27.093 --> 00:30.596
<i>by a call from Tim's mother</i>
<i>saying she was dying.</i>

00:30.597 --> 00:32.097
<i>Tim, who was sure</i>
<i>she was faking,</i>

00:32.098 --> 00:34.600
<i>decided to go to her</i>
<i>immediately...</i>

00:34.601 --> 00:36.101
<i>or by the weekend,</i>
<i>at the latest.</i>

00:36.102 --> 00:37.603
<i>Dutch had to go on the run,</i>

00:37.604 --> 00:39.104
<i>but planned to return</i>
<i>to see Eunice.</i>

00:39.105 --> 00:40.606
<i>And Chester,</i>

00:40.607 --> 00:43.108
<i>although he hadn't planned</i>
<i>anything of the kind,</i>

00:43.109 --> 00:45.110
<i>had an attack</i>
<i>and was rushed to the hospital.</i>

00:45.111 --> 00:46.612
<i>Confused?</i>

00:46.613 --> 00:47.613
<i>You won't be</i>

00:47.614 --> 00:50.116
<i>after this week's episode</i>
<i>of</i> Soap.

00:53.119 --> 00:56.121
<i>This is the story</i>
<i>of two sisters,</i>

00:56.122 --> 00:58.123
<i>Jessica Tate...</i>

00:58.124 --> 01:00.626
<i>and Mary Campbell.</i>

01:00.627 --> 01:02.629
<i>These are the Tates.</i>

01:04.129 --> 01:06.632
<i>And these are the Campbells.</i>

01:08.134 --> 01:10.636
<i>And this is...</i> Soap.

